It is NTR. Sagiri here have a feelings which she rather deny towards the actual protagonist, they don't need to be in relationships. Also by the time of this DOUJIN takes place, our protagonist knows that the girls had this more-than-like feelings towards him, though, only several people who read the manga with imagination will actually knows how to feel about this this.
